name: Sea Graze
description: Whatever your grazing taste, Sea Graze has got you covered. Choose from our selection of deli graze boxes for delivery direct to your door. Choose from: Charcuterie box , Cheese graze box, Meat & Cheese graze box, Burrata graze box, Gluten free graze boxes, Vegan friendly cheese deli box. To see the full range and to order yours for this weekend, visit seagraze.co.uk.  We deliver Thursday - Saturday with last orders being taken at 6pm on the day before delivery.  A limited number of boxes are available for each day, so please book early to avoid disappointment.
